###### SETUP ######
### SED ###
table SED "cf.sed"
intensity {ins} range 1e-1 to 1e5 eV linear
### MEDIUM ###
hden {hden} linear
### SPECIES ###
abundances GASS10
metals {Z} linear
no molecules
### SIMULATION ###
iterate until convergence
set dr 0
stop zone 1
set continuum resolution 3 # opacity+emissivity resolution
###### SAVE ######
### OVERVIEW ###
save overview "sim.ovr" last
### SPECIES ###
save species densities *temp all "sim.species" last
### SED / EMISSIVITY ###
save continuum "sim.con" units ev last
save fine continuum "sim.fcon" units ev last
### OPACITY ###
save total opacity "sim.opac" units ev last
save fine opacities "sim.fopac" units ev last
# save optical depths "sim.depth" units ev last
# save line optical depths "sim.olines" limit -30 units ev last # tweak this to find good optical depths
